cast.overview: A calamity at Dante and Randall's shops sends them looking for new horizons - but they ultimately settle at Mooby's, a fictional Disney-McDonald's-style fast-food empire.
cast.title: Clerks II

details.biography:
From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

Zak Knutson (born January 4, 1974, Detroit, Michigan) is a movie producer and actor. He has a company called Chop Shop Entertainment with longtime friend Joey Figueroa. He has worked with writer and director Kevin Smith on his films and DVD projects.
